572253_xlarge.png?m=1691824464", "created": 1644395909, "last_modified": 1691824464}, "last_reply_by": "Takizawa", "last_touched": 1738568627, "title": "二手 m1 m2 主板当家用服务器", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1108659", "created": 1738513716, "deleted": 0, "content": "众所周知苹果 m1 m2 兼顾高性能与低能耗\r\n而且目前网络上存在某些 macbook air/pro 拆机主板\r\n然后 m1m2 cpu 支持 linux\r\n那么 8 核的 m2 是否碾压一切嵌入式服务器\r\n\r\nbcm2712 bcm2711\r\nrk3566 rk3588\r\nn100 n5105\r\n好像没一个有能与装了 linux 的无头 m2 对垒", "content_rendered": "众所周知苹果 m1 m2 兼顾高性能与低能耗<br />而且目前网络上存在某些 macbook air/pro 拆机主板<br />然后 m1m2 cpu 支持 linux<br />那么 8 核的 m2 是否碾压一切嵌入式服务器<br /><br />bcm2712 bcm2711<br />rk3566 rk3588<br />n100 n5105<br />好像没一个有能与装了 linux 的无头 m2 对垒", "last_modified": 1738513716, "replies": 19, "id": 1108659}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2421/fcb1/436_large.png?m=1650095204", "name": "nodejs", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2421/fcb1/436_normal.png?m=1650095204", "title": "Node.js", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nodejs", "topics": 2555, "footer": "", "header": "Node.js is a platform built on <a href=\"http://code.google.com/p/v8/\" target=\"_blank\">Chrome's JavaScript runtime</a> for easily building fast, scalable network applications.", "title_alternative": "Node.js", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/2421/fcb1/436_mini.png?m=1650095204", "stars": 2925, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 436, "parent_node_name": "js"}, "member": {"id": 562972, "username": "importmeta", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/importmeta", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2018/6513/562972_mini.png?m=1733475592", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2018/6513/562972_normal.png?m=1733475592", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2018/6513/562972_large.png?m=1733475592", "created": 1637669069, "last_modified": 1733475592}, "last_reply_by": "zhw2590582", "last_touched": 1738569763, "title": "吐槽一下 Nest.js 太复杂了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1108703", "created": 1738557164, "deleted": 0, "content": "正在写个项目, 模块一多心智负担较大.\r\n\r\n略微吐槽一下,简直是现实版茴字有几种写法.\r\n\r\n1.把中间件拆成 Middleware,Guards,Interceptors,Exception,Pipes, 并且他们都能获取请求上下文(Request, Response), 并且有不同的顺序, 但同类别内也有顺序, 并且生命周期是如此的繁琐.\r\n\r\n[https://docs.nestjs.com/faq/request-lifecycle]( https://docs.nestjs.com/faq/request-lifecycle)\r\n\r\n2.封装一个三方 API 花样太多了.\r\n\r\n单独的 Service, Providers, Dynamic Module, ConfigurableModuleClass\r\n\r\n这里面还有分 Sync 和 Async 导入, Global 模块.\r\n\r\n3.模块系统是 Angular 那一套, 注册繁琐, 还会出现循环依赖.\r\n\r\n\r\n心智负担比 Spring Boot 高太多了.\r\n\r\nJS 的后端框架不像前端那样卷, 真希望能出个好用的.", "content_rendered": "<p>正在写个项目, 模块一多心智负担较大.</p>\n<p>略微吐槽一下,简直是现实版茴字有几种写法.</p>\n<p>1.把中间件拆成 Middleware,Guards,Interceptors,Exception,Pipes, 并且他们都能获取请求上下文(Request, Response), 并且有不同的顺序, 但同类别内也有顺序, 并且生命周期是如此的繁琐.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.nestjs.com/faq/request-lifecycle\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://docs.nestjs.com/faq/request-lifecycle</a></p>\n<p>2.封装一个三方 API 花样太多了.</p>\n<p>单独的 Service, Providers, Dynamic Module, ConfigurableModuleClass</p>\n<p>这里面还有分 Sync 和 Async 导入, Global 模块.</p>\n<p>3.模块系统是 Angular 那一套, 注册繁琐, 还会出现循环依赖.</p>\n<p>心智负担比 Spring Boot 高太多了.</p>\n<p>JS 的后端框架不像前端那样卷, 真希望能出个好用的.</p>\n", "last_modified": 1738557601, "replies": 19, "id": 1108703}]